<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Robert_E._Howard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=25" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<p><a name="Sources" id="Sources"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Robert_E._Howard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=26" title="Edit section: Sources">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Sources</span></h3>
<div class="references-small">
<p><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFBlosser1997">Blosser, Fred (1997). "<i>The Star Rover</i> and 'The People of the Night'". <i>The Dark Man #4</i>: 16–18.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=%27%27The+Star+Rover%27%27+and+%27The+People+of+the+Night%27&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Dark+Man+%234&amp;rft.aulast=Blosser&amp;rft.aufirst=Fred&amp;rft.au=Blosser%2C+Fred&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft.pages=16%E2%80%9318&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Robert_E._Howard"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></p>
